</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='837735' id='t-837735'>Thank you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='838965' id='t-838965'>Thank you for your backup singing.</span>
